2 things:<br />1. The PAL PPU is <em>not</em> an RP2C02(G) - it is an RP2C0<strong>7</strong>(G?).<br /><br />2. The PAL CPU clock rate is not 1652097.902Hz, but 1662607Hz.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=7">Quietust</a> — Sat Oct 08, 2005 4:50 pm</p><hr />
